		<link>https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org/discussion/feel-a-pop-then-pain-in-your-knee-it-could-be-an-acl-tear/
		
		<dc:creator><!--[CDATA[Joel Streed]]--></dc:creator>
		<pubdate>Sun, 20 Oct 2024 10:00:00 +0000</pubdate>
